# New Component Checklist

When creating any new React component in this project:

## File Structure

```tsx
// 1. "use client" only if needed (hooks, events, browser APIs)
"use client";

// 2. Imports: React types, third-party, internal utilities, local types
import { type VariantProps } from "class-variance-authority";
import { cn } from "@/app/_libs/utils/cn";
import { buttonVariants } from "@/lib/variants"; // if reusing shared variant

// 3. Local CVA variant (if not reusing from variants.ts)
const myComponentVariants = cva(
  "base-classes-using-semantic-tokens",
  {
    variants: { ... },
    defaultVariants: { ... },
  }
);

// 4. Props interface
interface MyComponentProps extends VariantProps<typeof myComponentVariants> {
  className?: string;
  children?: React.ReactNode;
}

// 5. Component — use forwardRef for reusable components
const MyComponent = React.forwardRef<HTMLDivElement, MyComponentProps>(
  ({ className, variant, ...props }, ref) => (
    <div
      ref={ref}
      className={cn(myComponentVariants({ variant }), className)}
      {...props}
    />
  )
);
MyComponent.displayName = "MyComponent";

export { MyComponent };
```

## Checklist Before Submitting

- [ ] File name is kebab-case
- [ ] Colors use semantic tokens only (no hex, no Tailwind defaults)
- [ ] Border radius uses named token (rounded-card, rounded-button, etc.)
- [ ] Box shadows use shadow scale (shadow-sm, shadow-md, etc.)
- [ ] Typography uses font-sans/font-serif/font-mono + text-{size}
- [ ] Variants use CVA (no inline ternary class switching)
- [ ] Animation uses Framer Motion with spring presets
- [ ] Responsive: mobile-first (base styles for mobile, md: for desktop)
- [ ] Accessible: semantic HTML, aria-label on icon buttons, focus ring visible
- [ ] Imports use path aliases (@/, @/components/, @/app/)
- [ ] If interactive → "use client" at top
- [ ] cn() used for all className merging
- [ ] forwardRef used if this will be used as a primitive/reusable atom

## Quick Color Reference

| Situation       | Classes                                                |
|-----------------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| Page background | bg-background                                         |
| Text body       | text-foreground                                       |
| Subtle text     | text-muted-foreground                                 |
| Card            | bg-card rounded-card shadow-sm                        |
| Primary button  | bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-button     |
| Input           | bg-background border-border rounded-input              |
| Success state   | bg-success-bg text-success-foreground rounded-badge  |
| Warning state   | bg-warning-bg text-warning-foreground rounded-badge   |
| Danger/error    | text-destructive or bg-destructive/15 text-destructive |
